=== Accepted Values ===
Real numbers (not expressions) or [[value keys|_Values]]

=== Appearance ===
A text box followed by a shorter text box

{{https://people.rit.edu/sms6462/mc/img/scalingNumberOption.png}}

=== Details ===
* The first box is the base amount (used at skill/class level 1)
* The second box is the additional amount per skill/class level
* These options can also be affected by [[Attributes|Attributes]]